posting_body: ['Welcome home to your private oasis, with many fresh updates.', "A perfect home for someone who's had it with sharing a house and wants something comfortable and manageable just for them.", 'Home is an easy walk to North Market, Webber Library, Tori44 Ramen, The Get Down Coffee, and parks along the Mississippi River.', 'For transit riders, this home is a short walk to the Metro C line, or routes 19, 5, and 22.', 'For cyclists, Victory Memorial Parkway is just down the block, and for drivers, a one car garage with 120v power and ample off street parking is provided.', 'For EV owners, 2.9kw Level 2 (240v) charging is installed.', 'Many efficiency and quality of life upgrades are featured in this home including:', 'Insulated double hung windows', 'Cellular window shades with blackout shades in the bedroom', 'Hybrid heat!', 'Gas furnace and super high efficiency Daikin heat pump lets you choose the cheapest heating fuel.', 'Super high efficiency air conditioning', 'Gas dryer', 'Higher efficiency clothes washer', 'High output gas water heater', 'Gas stove/range', 'Vented hood fan', 'Ceramic tile floors in the kitchen', 'Gleaming hardwood floors in the living room and bedroom', "'built in' booth in kitchen", 'Marble shower with adjustable height wall head and handheld head', 'Ceiling fans', 'Fenced yard', '50 mbps internet available from Centurylink', 'New sewer in 2022', '100 amp electric service', 'The small print: Owner screens for evictions, UDs, and criminal history within the bounds of City ordinances.', 'Referral from your current property manager is required.', 'Customer must have verifiable income of $4,800 per month Customer will handle yardwork including timely snow removal.', 'Customer pays all utilities.', 'Well behaved pets will be considered, please contact for pet policy.', 'Feel free to write with questions.']
